<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-80-0299 </DOCNO><TEXT>The formulations of the scalar, spinor and gauge fields on a curved randomlattice are discussed. A new fermion scheme - simplicial fermions - whichis more natural in the presence of gravity, is introduced. Some of thepropagators in D=2 are evaluated numerically and are compared with thecontinuum limit.</TEXT></DOC>